        <tr><th>Service</th><th>Typical Range</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
        <tr><td>Residential diagnostic</td><td>$89</td><td>Flat, waived if repair is authorized same visit</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Wine cellar zone sensor</td><td>$180 – $340</td><td>Dual-zone diagnostic via Marvel interface</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Wine cellar controller / zone repair</td><td>$240 – $460</td><td>When sensor replacement doesn't resolve</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Ice-maker descale + fill valve service</td><td>$280 – $440</td><td>Hard-water LA neighborhoods</td></tr>
